      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KENTUCKY DRIVE (5) missed narrowly over this course and distance two back before stretching to 1400m last start and sticking on fairly. She looks better suited back to this track and trip today and the figure she put up in defeat two back stacks right up. She looks the one to beat. RATTLE THE CAGE (4) was a very cheap purchase who looks set to out perform his sale price by a long way. His two trials coming into this have been great at Belmont and Ramoly sticks with him on debut. Finds a very suitable race and can make a statement right away. DIRECT DEBIT (2) comes here with some strong form under her belt, bumping into a couple of sharp ones recently. Faithfull rides now and and she looks to get every possible. Form stands out and she can notch up her maiden win. WHITE HOT (6) finds a suitable race today and can make an impression. IT'S TRICKY (8) can sit closer this time and won't be far away.",
